synergyviewcore.timebar.component

Interface MediaControlBar.MediaControlListener

  • Enclosing class:
    MediaControlBar

    public static interface MediaControlBar.MediaControlListener
    The listener interface for receiving mediaControl events. The class that is interested in processing a mediaControl event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addMediaControlListener method. When the mediaControl event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    See Also:
    MediaControlEvent
